        <actionPlanTemplateItemValue>
            <itemEntityType>Task</itemEntityType>
            <name>Description</name>
            <valueLiteral>Complete the following items as the SUN is FINAL/Complete:

Modify from Prospect to Customer
Update Services sold to reflect signed contract terms (as needed)
Ensure data entered correctly &amp; reflects signed contract terms
Check the box for &apos;Contract Active&apos; 
Modify from Startup to TSG Contract 
If applicable, check the &apos;Leased Employees&apos; checkbox
Ensure SCP, Facility, or Third Party is entered for &apos;If Leased employees Ins Provided By&apos;
If applicable, check the box for &apos;Tele Services Active&apos;
If applicable, ensure accurate date entered and reflects terms for &apos;Tele Services Start Date&apos;
If there is a BAA, check the box
If applicable, check the &apos;BAA Declined by Facility&apos; checkbox
Offshore Prohibitions &amp; Description - ensure date is entered correctly &amp; reflects signed contract terms
Non-solicit &amp; Non-solicit type - ensure date is entered and correctly reflects signed contract terms
Non-compete &amp; Non-compete Type: Ensure data is entered and correctly reflects signed contract terms</valueLiteral>
        </actionPlanTemplateItemValue>
        <actionPlanTemplateItemValue>
